casebody.data:
Ronald Thompson CORBETT
v.
Pat MCCRORY, Governor No. 317P16-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 22, 2016 Ronald Thompson Corbett, For Corbett, Ronald Thompson. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 22nd of September 2016 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 22nd of September 2016."
